### 应用级权限与组织治理（平台 JWT + 应用库内 AppRole / AppPermission）
### 覆盖：创建租户应用实例后的默认角色/权限播种、成员管理、应用角色 DataScope、页面与字段权限。
### 平台侧写接口需 CSRF；应用 appKey 须全局唯一，冲突时请修改 @newAppKey。
### 成员接口 userIds 为平台用户 Id 字符串（示例使用 "1" 表示 bootstrap 管理员，可按环境替换）。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5001
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@adminUser = admin
@adminPassword = P@ssw0rd!
@newAppKey = apppremhttp2026x
@clientType = WebH5
@clientPlatform = Web
@clientChannel = Browser
@clientAgent = Chrome
@localeZh = zh-CN
@noAppPermUsername = http_no_apps_perm
@noAppPermPassword = P@ssw0rd!2026

### 管理员登录（需 AppsView / AppsUpdate / AppMembersUpdate / AppRoles* 等平台权限）
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}
Accept-Language: {{localeZh}}

{
  "username": "{{adminUser}}",
  "password": "{{adminPassword}}"
}

###
@adminToken = {{adminLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### CSRF
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

###

### 创建应用实例（触发 AppBootstrap：默认 AppAdmin/AppMember、应用权限码、根部门、创建者应用角色）
# @name createTenantApp
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "appKey": "{{newAppKey}}",
  "name": "HTTP 应用权限探测",
  "description": "AppPermissions.http",
  "category": "Test",
  "icon": "appstore",
  "dataSourceId": 1
}

###
@testAppId = {{createTenantApp.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 治理总览（应含系统预置角色、成员覆盖等统计）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/governance-overview
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 按 Code 定位 AppAdmin（默认全量应用权限 + DataScope All）
# @name listAppAdminRole
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles?keyword=AppAdmin&pageIndex=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@appAdminRoleId = {{listAppAdminRole.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 按 Code 定位 AppMember（默认仅 view 类权限 + DataScope OnlySelf）
# @name listAppMemberRole
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles?keyword=AppMember&pageIndex=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###
@appMemberRoleId = {{listAppMemberRole.response.body.$.data.items[0].id}}

### 列举应用内已播种的权限定义（应与 Bootstrap 默认码一致，条数 > 0）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织工作区（需 Permission:apps:view）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/organization/workspace?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 读取 AppAdmin 数据范围（预期 dataScope 0 = All）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appAdminRoleId}}/data-scope
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 读取 AppMember 数据范围（预期 dataScope 5 = OnlySelf）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appMemberRoleId}}/data-scope
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 将 AppMember 数据范围调整为 CurrentTenant(1)（验证 PUT；可按需改回 5）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appMemberRoleId}}/data-scope
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "dataScope": 1,
  "deptIds": []
}

### 可分配页面列表（低代码页面）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/available-pages
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppAdmin 已分配页面 Id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appAdminRoleId}}/pages
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### AppMember 页面权限（读取）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appMemberRoleId}}/pages
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 应用角色 — 字段权限读取（AppAdmin）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appAdminRoleId}}/field-permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 应用角色 — 字段权限全量替换为空（清空 AppMember 字段级覆盖）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/{{appMemberRoleId}}/field-permissions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "groups": []
}

### 可选动态表列表（字段权限配置入口）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles/available-dynamic-tables
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 成员管理 — 将平台用户加入应用（需 Permission:apps:members:update）
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/organization/members
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "userIds": ["1"],
  "roleIds": [],
  "projectIds": []
}

### —— 反向：无平台「应用」相关权限的用户 ——

### 创建无平台角色的用户（不含 apps:view 等）
# @name createNoAppPermUser
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{noAppPermUsername}}",
  "password": "{{noAppPermPassword}}",
  "displayName": "HTTP 无应用权限用户",
  "email": "http.no.apps@atlas.local",
  "phoneNumber": "13800000003",
  "isActive": true,
  "roleIds": [],
  "departmentIds": [],
  "positionIds": []
}

###
@noAppPermUserId = {{createNoAppPermUser.response.body.$.data.id}}

### 无应用权限用户登录
# @name noAppPermLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
X-Client-Type: {{clientType}}
X-Client-Platform: {{clientPlatform}}
X-Client-Channel: {{clientChannel}}
X-Client-Agent: {{clientAgent}}

{
  "username": "{{noAppPermUsername}}",
  "password": "{{noAppPermPassword}}"
}

###
@noAppPermToken = {{noAppPermLogin.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### [反向 403] 无应用权限 — 组织工作区
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/organization/workspace?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{noAppPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 403] 无应用权限 — 应用角色列表
# @expected-status 403
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/roles?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{noAppPermToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### [反向 401] 未认证 — 应用权限列表
# @expected-status 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{testAppId}}/permissions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=5
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
